partnerDetails.about: Welcome to Northside Electrical Wholesalers, Northside Electrical was established by Kevin Sparg in 1995 and today is the leader in wholesale premium branded electrical, lighting & security goods. We supply products to leading property developers, electrical and building contractors, municipalities, retail outlets and the general public, for all industrial, commercial and domestic projects.
